Cybersecurity
The practice of ensuring confidentiality, integrity and avalability of information by protecting networks,
devices, people, and data from unauthorized access or criminal exploitation.

Threat Actor
Any person or group who presents a security risk

Benefits of security
1. Protects against external and internal threats
2. Meets regulatory compliance
3. Maintains and improves business productivity
4. Reduces expenses
5. Maintains brand trust

Common job titles
1. Security analyst or specialist
2. Cybersecurity analyst or specialist 
3. Security operations center (SOC) analyst
4. Information security analyst
